    {"type":"text","id":"np_h","x":20,"y":152,"width":320,"height":22,"text":"PRUEBAS NO PARAMÉTRICAS","originalText":"PRUEBAS NO PARAMÉTRICAS","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#7f1d1d","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":2401,"version":1,"versionNonce":2402,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"np_c","x":28,"y":178,"width":304,"height":158,"text":"2 grupos independientes:\n→ Mann-Whitney U\n   (basado en rangos)\n\n2 grupos pareados:\n→ Wilcoxon signed-rank\n   (diferencias por rango)\n\n3+ grupos:\n→ Kruskal-Wallis\n   (equivalente no-param de ANOVA)\n\nDatos ordinales, n<30,\nno normales, outliers extremos","originalText":"2 grupos independientes:\n→ Mann-Whitney U\n   (basado en rangos)\n\n2 grupos pareados:\n→ Wilcoxon signed-rank\n   (diferencias por rango)\n\n3+ grupos:\n→ Kruskal-Wallis\n   (equivalente no-param de ANOVA)\n\nDatos ordinales, n<30,\nno normales, outliers extremos","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#991b1b","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":2501,"version":1,"versionNonce":2502,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.4},

