    {"type":"text","id":"pa_h","x":560,"y":152,"width":320,"height":22,"text":"PRUEBAS PARAMÉTRICAS","originalText":"PRUEBAS PARAMÉTRICAS","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#064e3b","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":2701,"version":1,"versionNonce":2702,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"pa_c","x":568,"y":178,"width":304,"height":158,"text":"2 grupos independientes:\n→ t-test de dos muestras\n   (compara medias)\n\n2 grupos pareados:\n→ t-test pareado\n   (diferencias individuales)\n\n3+ grupos:\n→ ANOVA de una vía\n   (varianza entre vs dentro)\n\nDatos continuos, n≥30\no normalidad confirmada","originalText":"2 grupos independientes:\n→ t-test de dos muestras\n   (compara medias)\n\n2 grupos pareados:\n→ t-test pareado\n   (diferencias individuales)\n\n3+ grupos:\n→ ANOVA de una vía\n   (varianza entre vs dentro)\n\nDatos continuos, n≥30\no normalidad confirmada","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#065f46","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":2801,"version":1,"versionNonce":2802,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.4},

    {"type":"text","id":"fnote","x":20,"y":354,"width":860,"height":18,"text":"Conservadurismo: si dudas, usa no-paramétrica — casi igual de poderosa cuando se cumple normalidad, mucho más robusta cuando no.","originalText":"Conservadurismo: si dudas, usa no-paramétrica — casi igual de poderosa cuando se cumple normalidad, mucho más robusta cuando no.","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#475569","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":2901,"version":1,"versionNonce":2902,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25}
